Install:

Grab Hadoopy, use sudo setup.py install  - https://github.com/bwhite/hadoopy

sudo apt-get install python-dev
git clone git://github.com/bwhite/hadoopy.git
sudo python setup.py install

Usage:
bash run.sh


build.sh: Run to compile everything, the hadoop streaming class files are required
run.sh: Makes example data with Python, reads it with java (for frame output 'to hbase' testing).  The output from Java is unrelated, it is the video 'from hbase' and that is read in with Python.